        HOME_DESC: "<div className=\"row no-gutters\"><div className=\"col-md-6\"><span className=\"icon\">ðŸ™‹</span><h3>Most accurate personality test ever created</h3><p>Interpersonality isn't the same old personality test you get everywhere else. Our brand-new model was built with AI, using research finished in 2020.</p><p>Humans don't fit neatly into 16 personality types. That's why our model has <em>30 million</em> unique profiles.</p></div><div className=\"col-md-6\"><span className=\"icon\">ðŸ‘¥</span><h3>Similarity Score<sup>TM</sup> with friends</h3><p>With each of your friends, you can see a side-by-side personality comparison. Find out where you're similar and different.</p><p>You'll discover why you seem to 'click' with some people - and not others.</p></div><div className=\"col-md-6\"><span className=\"icon\">â¤ï¸</span><h3>Guide for Couples</h3><p>Based on your personality profiles, we can tell you what the <em>real</em> problems are in your relationship. They aren't what you think they are.</p><p>And 76% of your fights can be avoided entirely.</p><p>We show you how to <u>harness</u> who you already are - and who your partner already is - to create a relationship that works for the two of you. </p></div><div className=\"col-md-6\"><span className=\"icon\">ðŸ”®</span><h3>Romantic Compatibility Guide</h3><p>We can accurately predict the long-term romantic compatibility of you and your date.</p><p>We can tell you what problems you'll have, <em>how</em> you'll fight, and where personality matches will make things great.</p><p>This guide reveals things you'd only normally find out after years together.</p></div></div>",
